Package: pepVet
Type: Package
Title: Evaluate Proteolytic Digests for Proteomics Workflows
Version: 0.0.1
Authors@R:
    person("Enes K. Ergin", email = "eneskemalergin@gmail.com", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: Tools for simulating proteolytic digestion and evaluating
    peptide sets for proteomics workflows. The current repository state
    provides the initial Bioconductor-oriented package scaffold, dependency
    manifest, and testing surface for incremental feature development.
